steps.name: And Verify that cart page is displayed
And Enter the details in the Signup form from given sheetname "RegistrationDetail" and rownumber 1
And Verify ACCOUNT CREATED is visible and click Continue button
And Verify Login in as "hello" is visible
And Click Cart button from login page
And Verify Address Details and Review Your Order
And Enter description in "Deliver it soon" text area and click Place Order
And Enter payment details from given Excel Sheet "CardDetails" and rowNumber 1
And Click Pay and Confirm Order button
And Verify success message "Congratulations! Your order has been confirmed!"
Then Verify that Account Deleted is visible and click continue
